並且使你們信了，就可以因他的名得生命。」\\[0.4em]
{\itshape
A chapter-by-chapter study of all 21 chapters of John's Gospel,
integrating Elder Wong's teaching, John MacArthur's verse-by-verse
exposition, and G. Campbell Morgan's spiritual analysis —
framed by John 20:31's purpose: that you may believe, and believing,
have life in His name.}
